data.description: NOWS YOUR CHANCE to own an affordable Cape Code located in desirable Long Valley with top rated schools! Featuring a first floor Primary bedroom, 2 full baths, a country kitchen, sunroom, family room and living room; upstairs there is a loft with 2 additional bedrooms. This home boasts skylights, cathedral ceilings, wood floors and built in bookshelves throughout. Spacious basement with plenty of storage space, workshop area and a wood burning freestanding stove. In addition there is a beautiful level backyard with a roomy deck and a patio. This property needs updating and is being sold AS IS however the roof and Septic system are only about 6 years old. Appx 1887 Sq Ft per the NJ Tax records
